documentation.text:
@dev Allows user which has previously reserved `Registration` using `registrationId` to buy
 `name` for `_lockingPeriod` of time. Method accepts  payment with amount of `_advance` plus fee.
@dev Factory method for `Registration`.

Bought(address,string,uint256).details: It is emitted when `name` is bought.

Claimed(address,string).details: It is emitted when amount locked for `name` is claimed.

Renewed(address,string,uint256).details: It is emitted when  `name` is renewed.

ReservationCanceled(bytes32).details: It is emitted when  reservation with `id` is canceled.

Reserved(address,bytes32,uint256).details: It is emitted when `id` is reserved.

buy(bytes32,string).details: Allows user which has previously reserved `Registration` using `registrationId` to buy `name` for `_lockingPeriod` of time. Method accepts  payment with amount of `_advance` plus fee.

calculateFee(string).details: Calculates fee based on `_basePrice` and `name` length, returns `uint256`.

cancelReservation(bytes32).details: Cancels `registrationId` and returns `advance` amount minus `_cancellationFee`. `_msgSender()` must be owner of reservation.

claim(string).details: Claims `_lockingAmount` amount which is locked during the buy. Frees registration of `name` so it can be used again.

isAvailableById(bytes32).details: Checks if `registrationId` which is derived from `name` is available for registration.

isAvailableByValue(string).details: Checks if `name` is available for registration.

renew(string).details: Allows `_msgSender()` to renew already bought `Registration` for `name`. Renewals is available `_renewPeriod` before Registration expiration.

reserve(bytes32).details: Reserves registration identified with `registrationId` which is derived from `name`. Accepts as value `_advance`. Reservation last for `_reservationPeriod` period of time. If prior registration with same `registrationId` which `_reservationPeriod` is expired is fount it is canceled.
